title: Chapter supplemented by other law
context: [ยง526-4] Chapter supplemented by other law. (a) Unless displaced by a provision of this chapter, the principles of law and equity supplement this chapter. (b) This chapter does not limit any right of a person to waive, release, disclaim, or renounce an interest in or power over property under a law other than this chapter. [L 2000, c 43, pt of ยง1]
